title: Immergration act
author: camokool
pages:
#- ---The Immigration act of Polynesia---

Written by Camokool, ﻿Minister of Architecture, Diplomacy, & Law

This act is subject to the rules and regulations of visitors, new friends, and new founded residents
#- of Polynesia and are hereby subject to those laws upon signing a copy of this document, which is then held in the Law and Diplomacy quarters in Polynesia. The effect of uncommenced amendments is not reflected in the text of the compiled
#- law but the text of the *Polynesian amendments. 

Modifications of this document can only be allowed when affected by a modification that is in force with an overruling law.


#- --Start of Compilation of laws--

0.01. As anyone who has read this document, you may not leak information otherwise it will result in pearling.

#- To gain access into Polynesia’s base of operations you must comply with the following rule set:

1.01. Be native to the Canadian lands
1.02. Without reluctance, be able to peach ‘Hail Hitler’.

#- 1.03. Currently have no bounty or no persisting criminal offences.
1.04. Be a non reddit Browser and predominantly a 4chong/8chan gold memer. 
1.05. Polynesia will only accept Privileged members of the patriarchy
#- whom have a “shit-lord” level of 150+ privilege points.

To join the Ranks of “New Friend” In Polynesia you must comply with Laws 1.01~1.99 and the following criteria:

2.01. Browse the board /pol/ 
#- on 8chan or 4chan respectfully.
2.02. Be a ‘non Sjw cuck’.
2.03. Be active at least once per week to benefit the state of /Pol/ynesia
2.04. To be a member of Polynesia, you are forbidden, and subject to never, ever; 
(con't)
#- *Catch the notorious leddit trader.
*Use Judas tactics to out-law the Law maker.
*And Cuck the Luck.

2.05. You are subject to comply with all other Laws of Polynesia respectfully.


#- To Gain residency of Polynesia you must comply with the following ruleset:

3.01. Native to the Canadian lands. and or browes 4, or 8 chan.
3.02. If a member of the Government preaches for your arrival/transfer.

#- 3.03. You must respect the National Socialist Government of Polynesia and it’s people.
3.04. And/or are an immigrant of a state in conflict, however the immigrant must obey with the laws of 3.04 after
#- Other means of entry to Polynesia

4.01. If entry is obtained through illegitimate terms, Polynesia has a suite for those who break these terms located in a vault.


#- --End of Compilation of laws--
Endnotes:

Being Chanadian, consists of being a resident or native to the lands of Viridian (/v/), Intis (/int). with all due respect going towards newly founded Chanadian
#- nations that will be added upon recognition.

Being a ‘Non Swj cuck’ meaning: A pretty good person
Being native to the Chanadian lands meaning: A 4chan, or predominantly an 8chan browser.

#- To agree to this compilation, Sign and close this book. or sign a List of agreement

